  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A pilot study to observe satisfaction of analgesia with intercostal catheters after VATS
      lobectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Pain and satisfaction with pain treatment is investigated in a population after VATS
      lobectomy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
